    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Introduction"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To support memory protection which protects ASIL regions from QM access we have the following components."
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Service.OsHooks",
        "Service.ContextSwicher",
        "Aurix.SafetyManager"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Usually, any illegal memory access will end up in Trap. All Traps are processed by OS and we enter Safe State via Service.OsHooks module."
    },
